{"tid":1435783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府反擊，再唔諗出路就真係玩撚完！！","createTime":"2019-08-09T06:42:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T08:48:42.000Z","uid":300473,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a59e907e4c11a248f16866b76cad59f97b97fd65","tid":1435783,"uid":300473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>對付勇武</strong><br />\n諗住可以撚到啲狗攰，爆埋手足口病就好開心打晒飛機？<br />\n大陸已經開始<span style=\"color: red;\">搵武警/解放軍混入警犬</span>幫手，打持久戰對我方無好處。<br />\n拉咗嘅手足越嚟越多，<span style=\"color: red;\">再係咁落去好快會散</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>對付和理非</strong><br />\nWhatspp/ WeChat瘋傳放風會有黑社會刀手，狗屋拉閘，製做<span style=\"color: red;\">白色恐怖</span>。中間派同淺黃真係會驚，唔敢出嚟行。大家唔覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">出嚟嘅人越嚟越</span>少？<br />\n開始有人想<span style=\"color: red;\">搞大台騎劫運動</span>，有大台政府就可以搵人傾，收買中間派同勇武割蓆，所以一定唔可以有大台！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>反擊</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">去機場唔係去鳩坐，唔係去打狗！</span>大陸最撚驚啲豬知乜係民主，<span style=\"color: red;\">派下傳單</span>嚇鳩佢啦！<span style=\"color: red;\">佢唔比人去離境大堂就係咁解</span>！<br />\n機場咁大，唔去離境大堂都大把地方派！巴士站又得，機場快線又得，停車落客點又得！<br />\n不過我覺得今次<span style=\"color: red;\">一定會有人搞事</span>，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武今次要做盾</span>，好好保護兄弟！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58abcb4053414f4eee109ab855d2c0dd0d39d1c","tid":1435783,"uid":300473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ac502361696f9e8bd223d7661606885381bf8372","tid":1435783,"uid":266653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:37:38.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"496fb4aee90d22c7956980027cb10acb55fa8c0e","tid":1435783,"uid":266653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:37:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"70524417305deab3039b8317da03fca60731134c","tid":1435783,"uid":266653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:38:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7eeffab839e2932be9d1aafdbc4c8cf47b5b1c14","tid":1435783,"uid":266653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:38:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8733ef182a0a4679edd9160d27de14adebf8fd76","tid":1435783,"uid":266653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8e6480ece165464d82d5bb28acf538797556a81a","tid":1435783,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:39:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">去機場唔係去鳩坐，唔係去打狗！大陸最撚驚啲豬知乜係民主，派下傳單嚇鳩佢啦！佢唔比人去離境大堂就係咁解！<br />\n機場咁大，唔去離境大堂都大把地方派！巴士站又得，機場快線又得，停車落客點又得！<br />\n不過我覺得今次一定會有人搞事，所以勇武今次要做盾，好好保護兄弟！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"b5157121e8927735ad1917361d311323e89b0be8","tid":1435783,"uid":141576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:40:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dea47326b0b4038d8a3d230db8a2c5488ad7b3c4","tid":1435783,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"長氣d講句，唯有不斷吸納支持者先係正確既下一步<br />\n<br />\n好多巴絲係度煩緊下一步應該和理非繼續遊行 機場集會定應該行動升級包括不合作運動同勇武<br />\n<br />\n其實真係諗多左，我地不嬲都話冇大台各有各做，亦控制唔到其他同路人做乜，佢地選擇得果個行動就代表承擔得起個後果，每個人做之前亦應該思考下做完之後對件事有冇幫助，唔好人做你做<br />\n<br />\n同埋今次我覺得正苦同我地都低估左民怨情度，只要有鋪天蓋地既事實宣揚 有大眾既渠道將真相帶入屋，只有極少數既深藍會仲企係正苦黑警果邊"},{"pid":"6e641ff8d9bbad11683c64ef492080c044345ee4","tid":1435783,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:43:19.000Z","msg":"連派三日"},{"pid":"b41f61fc1f7d610c8dbe599a2000fbddb96eb4b3","tid":1435783,"uid":266839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:48:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}